00:01:06.925 --> 00:01:08.124 align:middle line:84%
MARCO BISCHOF
(THROUGH INTERPRETER):

00:01:08.124 --> 00:01:11.970 align:middle line:84%
Apocalyptic prophecies,
conspiracy theories,

00:01:11.970 --> 00:01:13.450 align:middle line:90%
and uh, so forth.

00:01:13.450 --> 00:01:20.294 align:middle line:10%
All of them aim at stirring up
emotions, positive or negative.

00:01:20.294 --> 00:01:21.160 align:middle line:10%
INTERPRETER: It's a cycle.

00:01:21.160 --> 00:01:22.500 align:middle line:10%
The Mayan cycle.

