00:14:57.060 --> 00:15:00.660 align:middle line:84%
by means of the electromagnetic
fields that they generate.

00:15:00.660 --> 00:15:04.060 align:middle line:84%
That these electrons, or
at least a certain hardcore

00:15:04.060 --> 00:15:06.180 align:middle line:84%
portion of them,
are the substance

00:15:06.180 --> 00:15:08.490 align:middle line:90%
of what we call the human soul.

