shown us that things

00:17:26.130 --> 00:17:29.070 align:middle line:84%
are much more interconnected
than we previously imagined.

00:17:29.070 --> 00:17:32.360 align:middle line:84%
I think this more
holistic approach

00:17:32.360 --> 00:17:36.120 align:middle line:84%
is the way science is going
and is bound to continue to go.

