NARRATOR: So, the cause of a
revolutionary transformation

00:22:48.442 --> 00:22:51.180 align:middle line:84%
in our perception
could indeed be a

00:22:51.180 --> 00:22:53.510 align:middle line:90%
colossal electromagnetic field.

00:22:53.510 --> 00:23:04.580 align:middle line:90%


00:23:04.580 --> 00:23:07.870 align:middle line:84%
When astronauts returned from
the first manned space flight

00:23:07.870 --> 00:23:10.240 align:middle line:84%
