Earth's magnetic field.

00:23:21.890 --> 00:23:28.070 align:middle line:90%


00:23:28.070 --> 00:23:31.150 align:middle line:84%
This fact shows with
stunning clarity

00:23:31.150 --> 00:23:33.630 align:middle line:84%
that our Earth's
magnetic field does

00:23:33.630 --> 00:23:36.555 align:middle line:84%
a lot more than just protect
us from cosmic radiation.

00:23:36.555 --> 00:23:39.060 align:middle line:90%


00:23:39.060 --> 00:23:41.860 align:middle line:84%
Our entire
bio-organism literally

00:23:41.860 --> 00:23:45.040 align:middle line:90%
harmonizes with this field.

00:23:45.040 --> 00:23:49.580 align:middle line:84%
It regulates the cycles
of life and our body clock

00:23:49.580 --> 00:23:51.480 align:middle line:84%
and could even be
the engine for many

00:23:51.480 --> 00:23:54.020 align:middle line:90%
of the metabolic processes.

