00:38:35.530 --> 00:38:38.340 align:middle line:84%
NARRATOR: And another thing,
on the morning of September

00:38:38.340 --> 00:38:42.350 align:middle line:84%
the 1st, 1859, British
astronomer and sun researcher

00:38:42.350 --> 00:38:45.260 align:middle line:84%
Richard Carrington
happened by coincidence

00:38:45.260 --> 00:38:49.345 align:middle line:84%
