governments the world
over are preparing more

00:39:40.580 --> 00:39:41.820 align:middle line:90%
or less for such a scenario.

00:39:41.820 --> 00:39:44.440 align:middle line:90%


00:39:44.440 --> 00:39:46.930 align:middle line:84%
But the possible effects
on our bio-organism

00:39:46.930 --> 00:39:48.970 align:middle line:84%
have largely been
ignored thus far.

00:39:48.970 --> 00:39:51.900 align:middle line:90%


00:39:51.900 --> 00:39:54.230 align:middle line:84%
Should we take the
ancient prophecies

00:39:54.230 --> 00:39:56.250 align:middle line:84%
of a quantum leap
in consciousness

00:39:56.250 --> 00:39:58.540 align:middle line:90%
seriously after all?

00:39:58.540 --> 00:40:01.480 align:middle line:84%
And not so much in terms of
mystic or spiritual parameters,

00:40:01.480 --> 00:40:04.230 align:middle line:84%
but quite pragmatically,
from a biochemical,

00:40:04.230 --> 00:40:05.360 align:middle line:90%
biophysical standpoint.

00:40:05.360 --> 00:40:09.910 align:middle line:90%


00:40:09.910 --> 00:40:12.105 align:middle line:84%
This is underscored
by a simple example.

00:40:12.105 --> 00:40:14.720 align:middle line:90%


00:40:14.720 --> 00:40:16.240 align:middle line:84%
Imagine that
someone were to give

00:40:16.240 --> 00:40:21.230 align:middle line:84%
you without your knowledge of
consciousness-expanding drug.

00:40:21.230 --> 00:40:23.440 align:middle line:84%
But as soon as the
substance takes effect,

00:40:23.440 --> 00:40:26.830 align:middle line:84%
you would begin to believe
you were losing your mind

00:40:26.830 --> 00:40:28.690 align:middle line:84%
because you would start
to feel and perceive

00:40:28.690 --> 00:40:33.930 align:middle line:84%
things that are not part
of reality as you know it.

00:40:33.930 --> 00:40:36.280 align:middle line:84%
If, on the other hand,
you were to take the drug

00:40:36.280 --> 00:40:38.630 align:middle line:84%
on purpose, fully
aware of its effect,

00:40:38.630 --> 00:40:40.410 align:middle line:84%
it would not take
you by surprise.

00:40:40.410 --> 00:40:42.840 align:middle line:84%
You would be prepared
for it and able to make

00:40:42.840 --> 00:40:43.775 align:middle line:90%
sense of the effect.

00:40:43.775 --> 00:40:50.540 align:middle line:90%


00:40:50.540 --> 00:40:52.620 align:middle line:90%
One step at a time.

00:40:52.620 --> 00:40:56.120 align:middle line:84%
Our brain is the interface
to our consciousness,

00:40:56.120 --> 00:40:59.050 align:middle line:84%
is also a high
performance filter.

00:40:59.050 --> 00:41:02.300 align:middle line:84%
The sensory organs deliver
around a million times more

00:41:02.300 --> 00:41:06.360 align:middle line:84%
information to the brain than it
passes on to our consciousness.

00:41:06.360 --> 00:41:09.180 align:middle line:90%
[ELECTRIC ZAPS]

00:41:09.180 --> 00:41:13.290 align:middle line:84%
Our brain decides how relevant
a particular sensory impression

00:41:13.290 --> 00:41:15.340 align:middle line:90%
is for our survival.

00:41:15.340 --> 00:41:18.390 align:middle line:84%
According to this prioritizing,
we are then either

00:41:18.390 --> 00:41:19.960 align:middle line:90%
able to perceive it or not.

00:41:19.960 --> 00:41:22.890 align:middle line:90%


00:41:22.890 --> 00:41:26.330 align:middle line:84%
Tranquilizers allow only the
strongest stimuli to reach

00:41:26.330 --> 00:41:27.485 align:middle line:90%
our consciousness perception.

00:41:27.485 --> 00:41:30.070 align:middle line:90%


00:41:30.070 --> 00:41:35.160 align:middle line:84%
Some psychoactive substances
have just the opposite effect.

00:41:35.160 --> 00:41:38.430 align:middle line:84%
Cannabis, for example,
disrupts the ability

00:41:38.430 --> 00:41:41.610 align:middle line:84%
of the visual system to
block out superfluous views

00:41:41.610 --> 00:41:43.210 align:middle line:90%
of the surroundings.

00:41:43.210 --> 00:41:46.450 align:middle line:84%
But hallucinations, such
as those induced by hashish

00:41:46.450 --> 00:41:49.020 align:middle line:90%
consumption, are not delusions.

00:41:49.020 --> 00:41:52.620 align:middle line:84%
Rather they are hyperrealistic,
uncensored images

00:41:52.620 --> 00:41:53.930 align:middle line:90%
one after the other.

00:41:53.930 --> 00:41:57.750 align:middle line:84%
Just as our brain constantly
registers them, but without

00:41:57.750 --> 00:42:00.520 align:middle line:84%
forwarding them on
to our consciousness.

00:42:00.520 --> 00:42:04.110 align:middle line:84%
LSD is another drug known for
its consciousness-expanding

00:42:04.110 --> 00:42:05.270 align:middle line:90%
effects.

00:42:05.270 --> 00:42:07.280 align:middle line:84%
Under the influence
of LSD, the ability

00:42:07.280 --> 00:42:10.595 align:middle line:84%
to perceive time and space is
lost within just a few seconds.

00:42:10.595 --> 00:42:13.550 align:middle line:90%


00:42:13.550 --> 00:42:16.380 align:middle line:84%
MICHAEL PERSINGER:
Structure dictates function.

00:42:16.380 --> 00:42:19.160 align:middle line:84%
All experiences come
from brain function.

00:42:19.160 --> 00:42:22.870 align:middle line:84%
And those experiences are due
to the structure of the brain

00:42:22.870 --> 00:42:25.730 align:middle line:84%
and the electrical patterns
associated with it.

00:42:25.730 --> 00:42:29.610 align:middle line:84%
You could imitate it by giving a
psychotropic drug, for example.

00:42:29.610 --> 00:42:31.950 align:middle line:84%
Or you can imitate it
by exposing the brain

00:42:31.950 --> 00:42:34.580 align:middle line:84%
to the appropriate
intensity temporally

00:42:34.580 --> 00:42:36.280 align:middle line:90%
patterned magnetic field.

00:42:36.280 --> 00:42:40.160 align:middle line:10%
For every molecular
pattern, called chemicals,

00:42:40.160 --> 00:42:43.770 align:middle line:10%
there is an electromagnetic
sequence or temporal pattern

00:42:43.770 --> 00:42:44.915 align:middle line:10%
that must be matched.

00:42:44.915 --> 00:42:46.670 align:middle line:84%
And when you apply
that to the brain,

00:42:46.670 --> 00:42:48.760 align:middle line:84%
you should get
comparable experiences.

00:42:48.760 --> 00:42:49.760 align:middle line:90%
And that's what we have found.

00:42:49.760 --> 00:42:52.950 align:middle line:84%
NARRATOR: The human brain
produces a neurotransmitter,

00:42:52.950 --> 00:42:56.990 align:middle line:90%
