00:43:28.320 --> 00:43:36.460 align:middle line:90%


00:43:36.460 --> 00:43:39.820 align:middle line:84%
Is it not plausible that
our brain is already

00:43:39.820 --> 00:43:42.180 align:middle line:84%
equipped with all
the prerequisites

00:43:42.180 --> 00:43:44.870 align:middle line:90%
for an expanded consciousness?

00:43:44.870 --> 00:43:47.740 align:middle line:84%
And that this, let's
call it function,

00:43:47.740 --> 00:43:51.110 align:middle line:84%
need only be activated by the
release of certain messenger

00:43:51.110 --> 00:43:54.980 align:middle line:90%
substances, such as DMT?

00:43:54.980 --> 00:43:59.020 align:middle line:84%
Molecules that weaken the
limitations in our perception

00:43:59.020 --> 00:44:00.530 align:middle line:84%
or even dissolve
them altogether.

00:44:00.530 --> 00:44:03.040 align:middle line:90%


